ame":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1775061229568,"sessionId":"f71634d9-8eb8-480a-b18d-826be75a9a17","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":44784,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/f71634d9-8eb8-480a-b18d-826be75a9a17.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check if there are active sessions first."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5fl77uz894vw_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775061230060}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775061234266}}
{"type":"message","id":"01074fe6","parentId":"a43a11ab","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:33:58.477Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session found is the current cron session itself. There's no active user conversation in the last 5 minutes. So I should proceed with the self-learning task - searching for latest news on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network systems integration, and IT operations services relevant to DaoJian Network.\n\nLet me use the web search skill to find this information.","thinkingSignature":"a27ca43071e579057632a31ff680772215d91f89d095c0e149f072cad10b8bbc"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到当前只有 cron 自身 session，没有活跃用户对话，执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9wilvjsicaas_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":809,"output":132,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44922,"cost":{"input":0.0002427,"output":0.0001584,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017205299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775061234269}}
{"type":"message","id":"6192b32f","parentId":"01074fe6","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:33:58.485Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9wilvjsicaas_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775061238481}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd8908c8","parentId":"6192b32f","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:34:02.638Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll search for the latest information on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network systems integration, and IT operations services in China.","thinkingSignature":"b561ac692258aa08554be84567f9af8fbef2fef093fa5876c7f747d5d27f9162"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y7256ywwygy5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新政策动态\" 2>&1; echo \"---EXIT:$?\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y7256ywwygy5_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026发展趋势\" 2>&1; echo \"---EXIT:$?\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y7256ywwygy5_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务行业发展趋势 2026\" 2>&1; echo \"---EXIT:$?\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1456,"output":178,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45615,"cost":{"input":0.0004368,"output":0.0002136,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0019698299999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775061238484}}
